OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist soon clearing then a
OL,6,Fdry day with long spells of sunshine.
OL,7,FBecoming quite warm inland but cooler
OL,8,Fwith some mist along the east coast.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA sunny evening for most but
OL,11,Fsome low cloud will affect the east.
OL,12,FDry with clear spells and becoming
OL,13,Frather chilly overnight with some low
OL,14,Fcloud spreading inland.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FEarly low cloud will mostly
OL,17,Fburn off but some will continue to
OL,18,Fafflict the coasts. Otherwise, another
OL,19,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine and
OL,20,Fbecoming warm inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
